{"tid":1018702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三年之後(2022年)  粵港澳大灣區三流 人流、物流、資金流便捷流通","createTime":"2019-02-12T12:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T18:20:41.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3724394bf0b5cffbe0c666b3b38ebde23e9d4378","tid":1018702,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:09:11.000Z","msg":"三年之後 粵港澳大灣區三流貫通<br />\n<br />\n廣東省發改委主任葛長偉昨天在廣東省兩會上表示，廣東省已經編制「實施粵港澳大灣區規劃綱要的實施意見和三年行動計劃」，將會在近期發布，他表示2022年粵港澳三地的市場規則將會對接，至2035年大灣區會將會全面建成。<br />\n<br />\n據21世紀經濟報導，中共國務院在2016年3月將粵港澳大灣區納入「十三五」規劃至今，當局未公布具體的規劃綱要。不過，葛長偉表示，廣東當局已經制定了大灣區的行動計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n葛長偉表示，從現在至明年，將會在大灣區規劃綱要的基礎上，再編制具體的專項規劃，包括國際創新科技中心、生態合作等，而今年上半年，則會公佈大灣區城市之間的軌道交通規劃。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">在2022年將要基本形成粵港澳三地規則對接，他表示這是大灣區建設的「重中之重」，讓到三地人流、物流、資金流可以便捷流通。</span><br />\n<br />\n葛長偉又稱，今年廣東當局將會積極推進粵港澳大灣區建設，包括推進河套地區港深科技創新園區、橫琴粵澳合作中醫藥科技產業園等建設，積極申報創建國家級重大科學裝置，除今年開通的蓮塘香園圍口岸，還會推動包括珠澳新通道、虎門二橋等交通基建建成通車。<br />\n<br />\n一是組織建設港珠澳大橋通信設施。中國電信、中國移動和中國聯通都在建設跨境傳輸光纜系統，已經實現港珠澳大橋以及東西人工島的無線覆蓋。<br />\n<br />\n二是完善通信網路布局。工信部在廣州、深圳、珠海設立了通信業務的出入口局，在深圳、珠海、汕頭有多個通信信道的出入口局，以實現粵港澳通信網路互聯互通。<br />\n<br />\n三是不斷提升通信能力。中國電信、中國移動、中國聯通在深圳、廣州、珠海等都建有多條跨境光纜，實現與香港、澳門多家港澳運營通信企業的互聯互通。<br />\n&lt;聯合報 &gt;"},{"pid":"50449cf14c2654f18b4651961fcad65fd95d1ebe","tid":1018702,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:20:49.000Z","msg":"一國一制"},{"pid":"902c11b6578512deb3aa8fdc53bbbf1ee9e512ca","tid":1018702,"uid":127569,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:30:19.000Z","msg":"最基本連私家車都做唔到互通啦，仲話咩通咩通，得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a6e1731eec8f98bae130677f9f27bf83104bea","tid":1018702,"uid":79023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"902c11b6578512deb3aa8fdc53bbbf1ee9e512ca","tid":1018702,"uid":127569,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:30:19.000Z","msg":"最基本連私家車都做唔到互通啦，仲話咩通咩通，得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:33:50.000Z","msg":"到時拆撚左啦邊境，同埋左軚車依家香港成日見啦"},{"pid":"df7100c90476b2fd58d5382ffc6aee4ec2df2e1f","tid":1018702,"uid":80217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:34:36.000Z","msg":"屌你 大灣區 3個字"},{"pid":"5986ff58746d306473a282e69ac8efd2d9d78ae4","tid":1018702,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:36:04.000Z","msg":"何必人地鳩叫下口號就氣急敗壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個城市都想做頭，點會傾得成"},{"pid":"2ae826ec398305c459cb85770c71592ad74bdf0f","tid":1018702,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:39:40.000Z","msg":"到時香港坐地鐵可以去到廣州"},{"pid":"71dacd60f0db0fe38767025f67ac0607df160c40","tid":1018702,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:43:38.000Z","msg":"人流-----會唔會向大灣區居民發&quot;大灣區證件&quot;?"},{"pid":"d9169e97fffbf28956dda1393d66a0b894ade9fc","tid":1018702,"uid":44358,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:50:58.000Z","msg":"再唔廢除香港關係法，美國變相資助中蟈科技升級，到時就算關稅收100%，都冇辦法再阻止邪惡出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836d5db413193be3101a26fcc15ace164a76127b","tid":1018702,"uid":43041,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:52:09.000Z","msg":"連登仔前排打曬飛機話中國唔敢再提大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒車不留餘力"},{"pid":"499c46dcd5230dd8a25ba2839d955e1057ba6bdc","tid":1018702,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:53:59.000Z","msg":"香港關係法倒數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad9f778e9281b005839582b88d9de6fd9d55d1f","tid":1018702,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:53:59.000Z","msg":"人民質素九流"},{"pid":"23da8fdef3a20a5dc7b5ea7f8301615e85e9830d","tid":1018702,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:57:31.000Z","msg":"香港融入大灣區 影響與美國關係？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">由中共中央成立的粤港澳大灣區建設領導小組8月15日在北京召開首次會議。外界一直懮慮，香港融入大灣區可能抵觸&ldquo;美國-香港關係法&rdquo;的條款</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/gf3-08152018093855.html/ampRFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fgangtai%2Fgf3-08152018093855.html%2FampRFA&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIulm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=c082ff43\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/gf3-08152018093855.html/ampRFA</a><br />\n(殘體)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國會報告<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong continues on the path of greater economic integration <br />\nwith the Mainland. The Hong Kong government has sought to <br />\nposition Hong Kong as a regional hub for China&rsquo;s Belt and Road <br />\nInitiative and a key node of the Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macau <br />\nGreater Bay Area integration project, Beijing&rsquo;s plan to establish <br />\na globally competitive advanced manufacturing, finance, and <br />\ntechnology center.<br />\n<br />\n報告摘要（英文）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uscc.gov/sites/default/files/Annual_Report/Chapters/Chapter 3 Section 4- China and Hong Kong_0.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscc.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FAnnual_Report%2FChapters%2FChapter%203%20Section%204-%20China%20and%20Hong%20Kong_0.pdf&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIulm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=e27977f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.uscc.gov/sites/default/files/Annual_Report/Chapters/Chapter 3 Section 4- China and Hong Kong_0.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"7019cecb3d9182a4fa029df266424188f75c30ca","tid":1018702,"uid":36551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:04:12.000Z","msg":"支持大灣區獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3906a67e315f8b4c336f399545934d94da8d0a97","tid":1018702,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:05:48.000Z","msg":"要求美國立大灣區關係法<br />\n將大灣區視為獨立關稅區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f81552f9e16aa4b6f7e9884976683dfbf5aac97","tid":1018702,"uid":163801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3906a67e315f8b4c336f399545934d94da8d0a97","tid":1018702,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:05:48.000Z","msg":"要求美國立大灣區關係法<br />\n將大灣區視為獨立關稅區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T13:11:12.000Z","msg":"阿邊個話獨立關稅區係寫喺基本法度，<br />\n嗌阿豬阿狗解釋吓就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7601b48383d5ba79896d02116e03155b4cc94657","tid":1018702,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23da8fdef3a20a5dc7b5ea7f8301615e85e9830d","tid":1018702,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:57:31.000Z","msg":"香港融入大灣區 影響與美國關係？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">由中共中央成立的粤港澳大灣區建設領導小組8月15日在北京召開首次會議。外界一直懮慮，香港融入大灣區可能抵觸&ldquo;美國-香港關係法&rdquo;的條款</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/gf3-08152018093855.html/ampRFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fgangtai%2Fgf3-08152018093855.html%2FampRFA&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIulm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=c082ff43\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/gf3-08152018093855.html/ampRFA</a><br />\n(殘體)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國會報告<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong continues on the path of greater economic integration <br />\nwith the Mainland. The Hong Kong government has sought to <br />\nposition Hong Kong as a regional hub for China&rsquo;s Belt and Road <br />\nInitiative and a key node of the Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macau <br />\nGreater Bay Area integration project, Beijing&rsquo;s plan to establish <br />\na globally competitive advanced manufacturing, finance, and <br />\ntechnology center.<br />\n<br />\n報告摘要（英文）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uscc.gov/sites/default/files/Annual_Report/Chapters/Chapter 3 Section 4- China and Hong Kong_0.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscc.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FAnnual_Report%2FChapters%2FChapter%203%20Section%204-%20China%20and%20Hong%20Kong_0.pdf&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIulm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=e27977f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.uscc.gov/sites/default/files/Annual_Report/Chapters/Chapter 3 Section 4- China and Hong Kong_0.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T16:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024d0d3024c407e0354f130ef1e9179880945a07","tid":1018702,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:15:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1239d16a315e80255cf80e8c577cc99cad3dc760","tid":1018702,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T18:20:41.000Z","msg":"香港庫房 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}